# GSD planning artefacts — private mirror only (see GitLab remote `private`).
# The public GitHub repo must not carry planning/roadmap/phase context:
# it includes decision logs, port analyses, and internal-fork references that
# are operational noise for external contributors. History was rewritten to
# remove .planning/ — do not commit it back here.
.planning/

# Helm — fetched dependencies live in charts/*.tgz and are reproducible from
# Chart.lock via `helm dependency update`.
helm/*/charts/*.tgz

# Integration test scratch — owned by the test harness, never commit
.venv-itest/
tests/integration/_tmp/
.pytest_cache/
sandboxd/
references/

# Translations / disposable readability copies — not for the repo
*-ru.md
*-ru-tmp.md
docs/architecture/manifesto/02-nfrs-ru.md

# Phase-research / review artefacts under docs/future-architecture/research/
# These are the working buffer the architect-loop produces while drafting
# canonical artefacts under docs/architecture/. They cite gitignored paths
# (sandboxd/) and carry phrases we don't want in committed prose
# ("reverse-engineered", "Anthropic-observed"). The canonical work in
# docs/architecture/ is the deliverable; these files stay local.
docs/future-architecture/research/SUMMARY-*.md
docs/future-architecture/research/REVIEW-*.md
docs/future-architecture/research/CROSS-REVIEW-*.md
docs/future-architecture/research/PLAN-CHECK-*.md
docs/future-architecture/research/CONTRADICTION-CHECK-*.md
docs/future-architecture/research/ADVISOR-*.md
docs/future-architecture/research/NYQUIST-AUDIT-*.md
docs/future-architecture/research/PATTERN-MAP-*.md
docs/future-architecture/research/CONSOLIDATED-*.md
docs/future-architecture/research/nfr-*.md
docs/future-architecture/research/layer*.md
docs/future-architecture/research/COMPETITOR-*.md
docs/future-architecture/research/PLAN-*.md
docs/future-architecture/research/RESEARCH-*.md

# Anthropic reverse-engineering digests — proprietary-derived material.
